{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CanvasGradient","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\">Canvas API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient\"><code>CanvasGradient</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient/addColorStop\"><code>addColorStop()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Canvas API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CanvasPattern\"><code>CanvasPattern</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmap\"><code>ImageBitmap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmapRenderingContext\"><code>ImageBitmapRenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/OffscreenCanvas\"><code>OffscreenCanvas</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Path2D\"><code>Path2D</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextMetrics\"><code>TextMetrics</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/createImageBitmap\"><code>createImageBitmap</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><code><strong>CanvasGradient</strong></code> インターフェイスは、グラデーションを記述する<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Opaque_data_type\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">不透明オブジェクト</a>を表します。 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/createLinearGradient\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D.createLinearGradient()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> または <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/createRadialGradient\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D.createRadialGradient()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> メソッドから返されます。</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/fillStyle\" title=\"fillStyle\"><code>fillStyle</code></a> または <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/strokeStyle\" title=\"strokeStyle\"><code>strokeStyle</code></a> として使用することができます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"プロパティ","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>不透明オブジェクトとして、公開されているプロパティはありません。</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"メソッド","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>継承されたメソッドはありません。</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"canvasgradient.addcolorstop_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient/addColorStop\"><code>CanvasGradient.addColorStop()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><code>offset</code> および <code>color</code> で定義される、グラデーションの新しい停止点を追加します。オフセットが <code>0</code> と <code>1</code> の間でなければ <code>INDEX_SIZE_ERR</code> が発生し、色が CSS の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/color_value\"><code>&lt;color&gt;</code></a> として解釈できない場合は <code>SYNTAX_ERR</code> が発生します。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/the-canvas-element.html#canvasgradient\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">CanvasGradient の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの対応","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.CanvasGradient","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a> のクリエイターメソッド</li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a> 要素と関連する <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a> インターフェイス</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"sect1\"></div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"プロパティ","id":"properties"},{"text":"メソッド","id":"methods"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの対応","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"CanvasGradient インターフェイスは、グラデーションを記述する不透明オブジェクトを表します。 CanvasRenderingContext2D.createLinearGradient() (en-US) または CanvasRenderingContext2D.createRadialGradient() (en-US) メソッドから返されます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CanvasGradient","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CanvasGradient","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CanvasGradient","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"CanvasGradient","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/canvasgradient","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/canvasgradient/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient","title":"CanvasGradient"}],"pageTitle":"CanvasGradient - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}